### Health
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### Login viewer
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "viewer@afristage.local",
  "password": "Viewer123!"
}

### Login creator
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "creator@afristage.local",
  "password": "Creator123!"
}

### Create coin purchase intent
POST http://localhost:3000/api/payments/coin-purchase-intents
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amountMinor": 100000,
  "currency": "NGN",
  "coinAmount": 1000
}

### Complete mock payment
POST http://localhost:3000/api/payments/mock/{{payment_intent_id}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_access_token}}

### Create live room
POST http://localhost:3000/api/live-rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{creator_access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Friday Night Afrobeats",
  "category": "MUSIC",
  "country": "NG",
  "language": "pidgin"
}

### Start room
POST http://localhost:3000/api/live-rooms/{{room_id}}/start
Authorization: Bearer {{creator_access_token}}

### Join room
POST http://localhost:3000/api/live-rooms/{{room_id}}/join-token
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_access_token}}

### List gifts
GET http://localhost:3000/api/gifts

### Send gift
POST http://localhost:3000/api/live-rooms/{{room_id}}/gifts
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "giftId": "{{gift_id}}",
  "quantity": 1,
  "idempotencyKey": "gift-test-001"
}

### Creator dashboard
GET http://localhost:3000/api/creators/me/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{creator_access_token}}

### Request payout
POST http://localhost:3000/api/payouts/request
Authorization: Bearer {{creator_access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amountMinor": 500000,
  "currency": "NGN"
}
